  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0b8e\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Always ready to serve the country",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa has stated in his resignation letter that he is always ready to continue serving his motherland.",
        "Parliamentary Secretary General Thammika Dasanayake submitted the President's resignation letter in the House today.",
        "He pointed out in the letter that due to the need to periodically shut down the country to protect people from the Corona pandemic in 2020-2021, the economic crisis and foreign exchange shortages that have been escalating over the years have been exacerbated.",
        "In his resignation letter, Kota mentioned that in order to resolve the resulting instability, all efforts were made to form an all-party or national government by inviting all political party leaders representing the Parliament.",
        "He also indicated that he will step down from the post of President from July 14th in accordance with the request of the general public and the leaders of the parliamentary party."
      ],
